  "name": "Dr. Emmett Brown",
  "nodeType": "CHARACTER",
  "description": "An eccentric inventor and nuclear physicist who has spent thirty years and his family fortune trying to build a working time machine. In 1985 he finally succeeds, using a DeLorean and stolen plutonium. He is shot by Libyan terrorists moments after the first test, but his younger 1955 self — initially disbelieving — helps Marty harness a lightning strike to power the return trip. His friendship with Marty transcends decades.",
